originalText.text: Spoke with a helpful rep about working for Southern Star and even all the mortgage programs they have. Very upfront about all their services they are there in the eye of the mortgage financial game, making their customers feel like stars! I went to a In house seminar they were very upbeat, did what they said and had a professional cordial staff to to go along with the star branding effect of service here! If I go for a mortgage SSM is on my priority list!
